channel.title: Error with new firemaking skill. [PI]
channel.description:
Hello! I get this darn error when I am using a new firemaking base.
[code] src\server\model\players\Client.java:886: error: cannot find symbol frame1(); ^ symbol: method frame1() location: class Client src\server\model\players\skills\Firemaking.java:57: error: cannot find symbol c.frame1(); ^ symbol: method frame1() location: variable c of type Client Note: Some input files use unchecked or unsafe operations. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:unchecked for details. 2 errors [/code] I know that the variable frame1 doesn't exist.. but what should I do to fix it?
I am using this tutorial: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,497591.0.html
